## Tailwind CSS Guidelines

### Mobile-First Responsive Design
- Design mobile-first, scale up using: base → sm → md → lg → xl → 2xl
- Example: `p-4 md:p-6 lg:p-8`
- Prefer relative units over fixed sizes

### Color System
Use semantic color tokens:
- Backgrounds: `bg-primary`, `bg-background`
- Text: `text-primary-foreground`, `text-primary`
- Borders: `border-border`

You can find all the design token related css variables in [globals.css](mdc:src/app/globals.css)

Example:
```tsx
<div className="bg-primary text-primary-foreground">Content</div>
```
